| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2319 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0bc64a0e-b609-5dd0-ba02-c1e5dd6856a6"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
